    "After that, the practical applications of deep learning point cloud registration in various fields are discussed, and some ideas about the possible development in the future are put forward.",
    "At present, the point cloud registration method of deep learning has made great progress, but it still needs to improve.",
    "At the end of this article, the future research direction and challenges are prospected.",
    "(1) Influence of point cloud density, scene noise and low overlap on the robustness of the registration methods.",
    "The point cloud data obtained in natural environment often has much noise, uneven distribution, and low overlapping."
